00:34.907 --> 00:36.842
Today is not Saturday.

00:36.876 --> 00:38.711
Why did you make me pancakes?

00:38.744 --> 00:40.947
They are fresh start pancakes.

00:40.981 --> 00:43.383
Like the first day
of school every year

00:43.416 --> 00:45.385
when you get to wear
a brand-new outfit.

00:47.620 --> 00:49.822
Well, not everyone
wore a new outfit.

00:49.855 --> 00:51.391
But the rule in this house

00:51.424 --> 00:53.859
is that when you start
a new life event,

00:53.893 --> 00:55.161
you get pancakes.

00:55.195 --> 00:59.365
I don't want a fresh start.

00:59.399 --> 01:01.234
I want to stay in surgery.

01:03.403 --> 01:04.604
I know.

01:04.637 --> 01:08.708
And I am really proud of you
for handling it all so...

01:19.485 --> 01:21.387
Doctors, please give me
one more minute.

01:22.288 --> 01:24.290
We have an associate pastor
at the church,

01:24.324 --> 01:26.826
but Clarence
likes to write the sermons.

01:28.128 --> 01:29.262
- Sorry.
- Please.

01:29.295 --> 01:30.796
Although this is important too.

01:31.831 --> 01:33.766
The surgery consists
of two steps.

01:33.799 --> 01:36.136
First we fuse the spine
to stabilize it,

01:36.169 --> 01:37.703
and then we remove the tumor.

01:37.737 --> 01:39.905
Because the cancer has spread
to your lymph nodes,

01:39.939 --> 01:41.341
you'll still have
to follow up with chemo.

01:43.609 --> 01:45.945
Clarence, are you in pain?

01:45.978 --> 01:48.581
Quite a bit actually,
but I'm fine.

01:48.614 --> 01:50.316
Well,
since what's causing your pain

01:50.350 --> 01:52.152
is the tumor pushing
against your spine,

01:52.185 --> 01:53.953
the spinal fusion will ease
pressure on your nerves

01:53.986 --> 01:55.155
and should eliminate your pain.

01:55.188 --> 01:58.624
Please, I, uh...
I need this pain.

02:00.193 --> 02:02.662
Can't you just do the second
part and remove the tumor?

02:02.695 --> 02:03.963
If we don't fuse the spine,

02:03.996 --> 02:06.566
it'll make removing the tumor
a lot more difficult.

02:06.599 --> 02:08.300
More difficult,
but it can be done?

02:08.334 --> 02:10.169
It can.
But I recommend against it.

02:10.203 --> 02:12.105
Especially since
there's no reason not to.

02:19.645 --> 02:21.547
I did something

02:23.649 --> 02:24.884
unforgivable.

02:27.019 --> 02:30.090
This pain is my punishment.

02:37.397 --> 02:39.832
Can I ask what you did
that was so bad?

02:43.136 --> 02:44.470
I killed someone.

